headline.main: Thirteenth Anniversary of the New-York Bible Society.; INTERESTING REPORT. Addressess by T. F. B. Merceln and M. Russell Thayer.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Annual meeting of the New-York Bible Society, auxiliary to the American Bible Society, was held yesterday evening in the Church of the Puritans, (REV. DR. CHEEVER'S) Union-square, at 7 1/2 o'clock. In the absence of H. K. BULL, ESQ , the President of the society, the Chair was occupied by E. M. KINGSLEY, ??., Vice President. The audience was slim.
